Frequency: once per day; 
Effect: Up to six of Angobo’s eyes detach from Angobo’s body. Each eye has AC 26, HP 1, and a fly speed of 40 feet. Angobo can see through all of their eye probes. They can move the probes all in separate directions using a single action. Angobo can have no more than six eye probes active at a time; using this ability to create more causes the eye or eyes farthest away to shrivel and die. 
Angobo can deliver touch spells through their eye probes and can make melee spell attacks through them. In addition, tAngobo can Steal Memories through an eye probe using a single action by touching the target with the eye.

Claw. 
Requirements: The Three-Faced Regent hit the same enemy with two consecutive Strikes of the listed type in the same round; 
Effect: The Three-Faced Regent automatically deals that Strike’s damage again to the enemy.
